              <span className="text-[8px] font-black text-emerald-500 bg-emerald-500/10 px-3 py-1 rounded-full border border-emerald-500/20">ENCRYPTION: AES_256</span>
              <span className="text-[8px] font-black text-indigo-400 bg-indigo-500/10 px-3 py-1 rounded-full border border-indigo-500/20">UPLINK: VERIFIED</span>
